{"tid":1723803,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有警員向記者說「我就係要搞你」江永祥稱語氣激動難免","createTime":"2019-11-15T09:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T12:09:56.000Z","uid":240362,"like":45,"dislike":291,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"142a3e5dd607348f54551eccfa57b00c8a8f8943","tid":1723803,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:38:42.000Z","msg":"對於有警員昨晚在東區走廊柴灣迴旋處要求檢查現場傳媒的證件，並表示「我就係要搞你」。警察公共關係科高級警司江永祥在記者會表示，當時警員希望盡快將暴徒繩之於法，所以語氣較激動，而另外有同事已即時代替相關同事處理。<br />\n<br />\n江永祥表示，過去多個月有太多突發、暴力事件，難免在語氣上會「較肯定」，舉例指警員在看燈飾、煙花等活動時，可以「笑住口」與市民溝通，但現時要使用較肯定的語氣，否則難以控制現場。<br />\n<br />\n另外，昨晚葵涌邨有防暴警員追截黑衣人至天橋升降機內，並要求在場記者關掉攝錄器材。江永祥回應說，若要求記者不要採訪是不符合規矩及指引，認為若記者有任何疑問歡迎投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492441-20191115.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492441-20191115.htm&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=3843f2a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492441-20191115.htm&h=4fd1d734\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492441-20191115.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d6b7ff9cce5125cbd2ae8d60bc760e1cf70e9001","tid":1723803,"uid":20396,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:39:25.000Z","msg":"肯肯定"},{"pid":"2a723abea73def087e568831103102257969bebc","tid":1723803,"uid":119250,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:40:28.000Z","msg":"黑警死兜爛兜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f771dc26230cff63110a6416a693fde7553a2b11","tid":1723803,"uid":194298,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:41:44.000Z","msg":"真係好撚核突依班object<br />\n完美形容無恥一詞"},{"pid":"17f7741995f8be318f54e066a4b0e719ec04aa9a","tid":1723803,"uid":144492,"like":77,"dislike":1,"score":76,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:41:58.000Z","msg":"無得兜就歡迎投訴<br />\n含撚啦