員會<br />\n所以我係咪可以屌你老母啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d126f92e8a49176227a2f17e96d9dddf2f230b","tid":1723803,"uid":152571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d57c9b0515974770fa04cfdb4343556999208eb9","tid":1723803,"uid":25468,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"142a3e5dd607348f54551eccfa57b00c8a8f8943","tid":1723803,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:38:42.000Z","msg":"對於有警員昨晚在東區走廊柴灣迴旋處要求檢查現場傳媒的證件，並表示「我就係要搞你」。警察公共關係科高級警司江永祥在記者會表示，當時警員希望盡快將暴徒繩之於法，所以語氣較激動，而另外有同事已即時代替相關同事處理。<br />\n<br />\n江永祥表示，過去多個月有太多突發、暴力事件，難免在語氣上會「較肯定」，舉例指警員在看燈飾、煙花等活動時，可以「笑住口」與市民溝通，但現時要使用較肯定的語氣，否則難以控制現場。<br />\n<br />\n另外，昨晚葵涌邨有防暴警員追截黑衣人至天橋升降機內，並要求在場記者關掉攝錄器材。江永祥回應說，若要求記者不要採訪是不符合規矩及指引，認為若記者有任何疑問歡迎投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492441-20191115.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492441-20191115.htm&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=3843f2a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492441-20191115.htm&h=4fd1d734\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492441-20191115.htm</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:44:03.000Z","msg":"點投訴 ? 蒙晒面又無 number"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:38:30.000Z","msg":"話之你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e436fbd7db84e575f530a95e79028d71130074d4","tid":1723803,"uid":247266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:40:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"395120da5d3e98885364d69cd379a32750e4ee4e","tid":1723803,"uid":88723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f0f961fd5409dbeaf215ff6457e615e2afc3932","tid":1723803,"uid":213917,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"dfe87802dcc9562cd83287a62c5012087198fb6c","tid":1723803,"uid":94771,"like":118,"di